Class RawDBObject

java.lang.Object
  com.mongodb.RawDBObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
DBObject, BSONObject
public class RawDBObject
extends Object
implements DBObject

This object wraps the binary object format ("BSON") used for the transport of serialized objects to / from the Mongo database.
